      "text": "（あれ……？　今、「けん玉姉さんだ！」って叫ぶ）\n（子供の声が聞こえた気がするけど……私のことかな？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Huh…? Just now‚ I heard a child's voice shouting）\n（'It's Kendama Sister!'… is it talking about me?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2666662853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
