      "text": "（ふふっ、「けん玉姉さん」っていい響きだな～）\n（声を掛けてくれた子はどこにいるんだろう～？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hehe‚ it's nice to hear 'Kendama Sister'~）\n（Where is the child who spoke to me~?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4999996186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
