      "text": "（わぁわぁ……どんどん子供達がkanaさんの所に）\n（集まってきてる！？　ど、どうしよう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wha-wha… More and more children are gathering around）\n（kana-san!? W-What should I do…）",
